edu.snu.onyx.runtime.common.optimizer.pass.runtime

Interface RuntimePass<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of the metric data used for dynamic optimization.
    All Superinterfaces:
    BiFunction<PhysicalPlan,T,PhysicalPlan>, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataSkewRuntimePass

    public interface RuntimePass<T>
extends BiFunction<PhysicalPlan,T,PhysicalPlan>, Serializable
    Interface for dynamic optimization passes, for dynamically optimizing a physical plan. It is a BiFunction that takes an original physical plan and metric data, to produce a new physical plan after dynamic optimization.
